After retiring from competition Schneider became a coach , leading the Canadian skeleton team to three medals at the 2006 Winter Olympics in Turin ( a gold for Duff Gibson , a silver for Jeff Pain and a bronze for Melissa Hollingsworth ) , and coaching Jon Montgomery to victory in the 2010 Winter Olympics in Vancouver , British Columbia , Canada . In July 2012 Schneider agreed a two - year contract to coach the Russian skeleton team .
